cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper presents a stochastic optimization algorithm for machine learning problems, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The paper specifically focuses on logistic and softmax regression, which are commonly studied in the machine learning community. Therefore, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.AI and cs.CV. Cs.NE and cs.DS are also possible sub-categories as they are related to optimization and machine learning.
